snippet.title: Johnny Depp Reacts TO BIG WIN In Defamation Case | Celebrity Craze
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Reacts To Win In Defamation Case | Celebrity Craze

For the past five years, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's relationship has been seen across the headlines. The details of their life together were revealed when a British newspaper branded the Pirates of the Caribbean star a "w-b", claims which he disputed. 

Johnny Depp does not seem to be stopping any time soon when it comes to finding any evidence that will support him in his libel case against his ex wife Amber Heard. Everyone is well aware of the fact that the two got a divorce, but it is clear that this has not been one that ended smoothly.

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #JusticeforJohnnyDepp
